  "title": "Innovative Light Turkish Split Peas Pilaf",
  "description": "A citrusy and light Turkish dish featuring split peas, perfect for a Jain-friendly meal, this pilaf is poached to perfection with a blend of aromatic spices and a hint of lemon",
